            <div>
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>UniSelfie was born from a simple idea: making photo experiences more engaging and memorable. Traditional photobooths felt limiting – cramped spaces, poor lighting, and restricted creativity.</p>
                <p>That's when I decided to revolutionize the photobooth experience with an open air approach. This setup allows for:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 1rem 0; padding-left: 2rem;">
